caption: Expensive for no reason. Maybe their rent is high; that would explain why the charge so highly for anything. This place is far from being fair with the prices. One drink could cost almost $4.00 over there while at other places it would barely more than half that price. And the staff can be so unpleasant; very poor customer service.
